Name: shouldProvideClusterScopeCapability()
Description: Should provide a MySQL DBMS capability at cluster scope

Name: shouldFailWhenNoLabelsProvidedForLabeledCapability()
Description: Should failed when a Labeled Capability was requested, but no Label Selector was provided

Name: shouldProvideNamespaceScopedCapability()
Description: Should provide a Capability in the same namespace when it is share with others in the namespace

Name: minimalDeploymentWithEnvironmentVariables()
Description: Should reflect both direct custom environment variables and environment variables referring to Secret keys

Name: shouldDeployCorrectPostgresqlImageWithDefaultSettings()
Description: Should translate the ProvidedCapability received to a TestResource and deploy it

Name: shouldLinkToExternalDatabaseService()
Description: Should link to external database service when all required fields are provided

Name: shouldProvideDedicatedCapabilityWithIngress()
Description: Capabilities could also have an Ingress to expose it to consumers outside of the cluster

Name: absoluteMinimalDeployment()
Description: Should deploy successfully even if only the image and port are specified

Name: requestSsoCapabilityOnDemandAndConnectToIt()
Description: Should request a required SSO capability on-demand and connect to the service using the resulting SsoConnectionInfo

Name: exposeHttpsServiceOverSpecifiedHostName()
Description: Should expose a service over HTTPS using the host name specified

Name: shouldProvideSpecifiedCapability()
Description: Should provide a capability with the specified name and namespace when the CapabilityRequirement specifies a scope of 'SPECIFIED'

Name: shouldProvideDedicatedCapability()
Description: Should provide a Capability that is dedicated to the resource on whose behalf it was requested

Name: createPersistentVolumeClaimUsingDefaults()
Description: Should create and mount PersistentVolumeClaims using defaults derived from the Entando Operator config properties

Name: shouldFailWhenThereIsAScopeMismatch()
Description: Should fail when the labels match but there is a scope mismatch

Name: shouldProvideLabeledCapability()
Description: Should provide a capability resolved at Cluster level using a Label Selector

Name: minimalDeploymentWithoutResourceLimits()
Description: Should deploy successfully with resource limits disabled

Name: shouldFailWhenTheCapabilityStatusPhaseIsFailed()
Description: The request for a new required Capability should fail if its deployment process ended with the 'FAILED' phase

Name: shouldFailWhenThereIsAnImplementationMismatch()
Description: Should fail when a matching ProvidedCapability is found but there is an implementation mismatch

Name: requestDatabaseCapabilityOnDemandAndConnectToIt()
Description: Should request a required database capability on-demand and connect to the service using the resulting DatabaseConnectionInfo

Name: createPersistentVolumeClaimWithGivenConfigs()
Description: Should create and mount PersistentVolumeClaims using the correct accessMode, storageClass and filesystem user/group overrides
